@page "/overview"

<PageTitle>DDD AspireShop</PageTitle>

<section class="shop-hero">
    <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">DDD AspireShop</p>
        <h1>AspireShop 云原生商城</h1>
        <p class="hero-copy">
            覆盖商品浏览、购物车、订单、秒杀、领域事件和 CAP 消息消费的 DDD 商城样例。
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="store">进入商城</a>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="flash-sale">秒杀专场</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="metric-grid">
    <article>
        <span>Domain</span>
        <strong>交易规则</strong>
        <p>商品库存扣减、订单提交、限购校验和值对象约束都进入领域或应用用例。</p>
    </article>
    <article>
        <span>Application</span>
        <strong>商城用例</strong>
        <p>MediatR 承载商品查询、普通下单、秒杀下单和领域事件派发。</p>
    </article>
    <article>
        <span>Infrastructure</span>
        <strong>消息驱动</strong>
        <p>订单提交后发布领域事件，再转换为 CAP 消息，由消费者消费。</p>
    </article>
</section>

<section class="commerce-roadmap">
    <h2>商城能力地图</h2>
    <div class="feature-strip">
        <span>商品分类</span>
        <span>搜索筛选</span>
        <span>购物车</span>
        <span>结算下单</span>
        <span>秒杀限购</span>
        <span>订单履约</span>
        <span>优惠券</span>
        <span>会员积分</span>
        <span>售后退款</span>
        <span>运营看板</span>
    </div>
</section>
